  "time_ut": 1632281131,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca  \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db3\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A manual coconut oil press machine at home",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A local inventor has been able to produce a hand-held coconut oil extractor at home without the use of toxins.",
        "YL, a government employee residing in Kekirawa Galkiriagama area of \u200b\u200bAnuradhapura district. The inventor Chandana Senanayake has made these hand machines using white iron.",
        "He said that this small hand machine for squeezing coconut oil has been developed according to the request of a local lord.",
        "At present, 18 people are employed and they are producing two types of small hand machines that squeeze coconut oil in the house.",
        "Mr. Chandana Senanayake said that one of these products can be used in a house for many years, a coconut oil extraction machine in pristine condition for a price of 6875 rupees and a product made for use in an ordinary house for 2875 rupees.",
        "As well as the increase in the prices of white iron and other materials, as well as the production of small quantities, if it is possible to buy large stocks of raw materials, it is possible to provide this equipment to the people at a lower price than this. He said that it would cost more.",
        "He mentioned that although the government has set aside a huge amount of money for many institutions to help the inventors, if they help for such things, this small coconut oil spraying machine can be given to every house at a very low cost and can be given to the needs of foreign countries.",
        "Those who are interested in getting machinery from this manufacturer can call 070 460 13 88 / 0 7 1 28 59 568 / 070 460 13 91."
      ],
